From: Chen Tessler <ctessler@nvidia.com>
Date: Mon, 9 Mar 2026 16:10:37 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 16/16] fix virtual gantry: match holosoma approach with root
 displacement + rest length

- Compute displacement from root body (pelvis), apply force at shoulders
- Add rest length (5cm slack) so spring only engages on larger drops
- Reduce gains (k=2000, c=400) to avoid extreme accelerations
- Eliminates competing torques from independent shoulder anchors

